<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Right side of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.32</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.37</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.50</measure>) with moulding above and below at the front and on the right face, and ahole for attachment on top.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on <term>fasciae</term> of upper and lower mouldings (ll.1, 2, 9), and on face, which is lightly drafted.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Lightly cut; second century A.D.; ave. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02</measure>; Ligatures: <foreign lang="grc">ΗΜ</foreign>ll.1, 5 ;  <foreign lang="grc">ΗΝ</foreign> ll.5, 8.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0200" exact="none">Second century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
